FEATURE_004 done. Changes shipped:

- **`layout.tsx`** — real estate title/description + `viewport` export with `themeColor` so mobile renders at correct width.
- **`page.tsx`** — soft slate gradient background, mobile-first padding (`px-5 pt-14` → `sm:px-6 sm:pt-24`), responsive headline/body, trust line under the form.
- **`LeadForm.tsx`** — 16px input font-size (prevents iOS focus-zoom), 48px input height + 52px CTA height for tap targets, prominent blue full-width CTA pill with shadow and focus ring, custom select chevron, asterisk for required field, polished success card with check icon.

No new libraries, no animations beyond `transition-colors`, no backend, no extra sections. `npm run build` passes; dev server returns `200` with viewport meta and all expected content. Report written to `.ai-build/last_build_report.md`.


